0My%20husband%20used%20Google%20Translate%20to%20communicate%20with%20them.%20We%20launched%20with%20about%20five%20bags%20per%20design%20and%20started%20marketing%20them%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20began%20posting%20videos%20online%20using%20trending%20audio.%20Eventually%2C%20one%20video%20gained%20traction.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20viral%20sensation%2C%20but%20it%20got%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20views.%20We%20sold%20out%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20felt%20like%20the%20key%20to%20e-commerce.%20I%20kept%20posting%20and%20grew%20my%20account.%20Even%20though%20we%20were%20based%20in%20Europe%2C%20our%20biggest%20traction%20came%20from%20the%20US.%20The%20American%20market%20made%20up%20almost%2050%25%20of%20our%20total%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20scale%20up.%20We%20dreamed%20of%20expanding%20beyond%20tote%20bags%2C%20launching%20other%20luxury%20items%2C%20and%20even%20homeware.%20We%20also%20focused%20heavily%20on%20growing%20our%20business%20in%20the%20US.%20Our%20ambition%20was%20to%20open%20a%20warehouse%20there%20so%20we%20could%20ship%20faster%20to%20our%20American%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20six%20months%2C%20we%20invested%20heavily%20in%20the%20US%20market%2C%20mainly%20through%20paid%20ads%20on%20Meta%20and%20other%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20more%20than%20%2432%2C000%20on%20our%20US-based%20campaign.%20We%20also%20gifted%20more%20than%201%2C000%20bags%20to%20creators%20in%20the%20US%2C%20covering%20the%20production%20and%20international%20shipping%20costs.%20It%20was%20a%20high-cost%20risk%2C%20but%20it%20felt%20worth%20taking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20until%20the%20tariffs%20came%20into%20effect%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c2c7a80-4ed2-463e-81cf-fe37546adb62%5C%22%3EInvesting%20in%20US%20sales%20felt%20like%20a%20risk%20worth%20taking%2C%20then%20tariffs%20hit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20overnight%2C%20our%20US%20sales%20drop