n%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20recruiter-in-chief.%3Cp%3EAndrej%20Sokolow%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20six%20recruiters%20and%20headhunters%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%2C%20all%20had%20worked%20on%20searches%20related%20to%20AI%2C%20mostly%20for%20tech%20companies.%20They%20said%20some%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20roles%20are%20AI%20engineer%2C%20machine%20learning%20engineer%2C%20agent%20software%20engineer%2C%20infrastructure%20engineer%2C%20research%20scientist%2C%20and%20the%20trendy%2C%20hybrid%20role%20of%20research%20engineer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecruiters%20see%20wildly%20different%20titles%20for%20the%20same%20work%2C%20though%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20their%20Canadian%20rival%20Cohere%20deliberately%20use%20the%20low-key%20%26quot%3Bmember%20of%20technical%20staff%2C%26quot%3B%20say%20True%20Search's%20Mark%20Bai%20and%20Shawn%20Thorne%2C%20to%20obscure%20what%20their%20teams%20are%20working%20on%20and%20protect%20against%20poaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20are%20still%20the%20hardest%20to%20find.%20The%20ideal%20candidate%2C%20headhunters%20say%2C%20has%20an%20advanced%20degree%20in%20machine%20learning%2C%20statistics%2C%20or%20mathematics%2C%20preferably%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F15-best-computer-science-programs-colleges-universities-united-states-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etop-ranked%20computer%20science%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%2C%20Stanford%20University%2C%20or%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%20A%20few%20years%20of%20experience%20at%20a%20tech%20company%20make%20a%20candidate%20more%20desirable%2C%20as%20it%20shows%20they%20can%20handle%20the%20long%20hours%20and%20high%20stakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20roles%20geared%20toward%20applying%20AI%20and%20wielding%20the%20stack%20effectively%2C