%20with%20her%20move.%20She%20enjoys%20traveling%20around%20Portugal%20and%20balances%20her%20work%2C%20including%20taking%20coaching%20calls%20for%20her%20new%20business%2C%20with%20social%20activities.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20just%20walking%20out%20my%20door%2C%20getting%20on%20the%20metro%2C%20crossing%20the%20river%2C%20and%20going%20to%20meet%20a%20group%20for%20a%20local%20meetup%2C%26quot%3B%20Stone%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20TikTok%20video%2C%20Stone%20wanted%20to%20send%20a%20message%20to%20other%20Americans%20who%20are%20worried%20they%20won't%20have%20enough%20for%20retirement.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20us%20played%20the%20game%20and%20followed%20all%20the%20rules%2C%20and%20we're%20coming%20up%20short%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20never%20too%20late.%20You%20have%20options%2C%20you're%20not%20alone%2C%20and%20you%20didn't%20do%20anything%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20recommends%20people%20interested%20in%20trying%20a%20new%20country%20to%20talk%20to%20their%20employer%20about%20whether%20that's%20feasible%2C%20like%20she%20did.%20She%20added%20that%20people%20don't%20have%20to%20take%20everything%20they%20own%20to%20their%20new%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStone%20also%20suggests%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-us-to-uk-culture-surprises-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmericans%20who%20are%20considering%20a%20move%20abroad%20%3C%2Fa%3Evisit%20beforehand%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20haven't%20traveled%20out%20of%20the%20country%20before%2C%20and%20not%20to%20expect%20the%20country%20to%20be%20like%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20point%20of%20moving%20somewhere%20else%20is%20to%20experience%20their%20way%20of%20living%2C%26quot%3B%20Stone%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-portugal-affordability-retirement-fears-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Ins